1) Necro pets 60+ are unfearable. No resist will ever be used as they can't be feared (though blind, if it sticks) will act as a fear,<br>
2) Lifetaps gets a -200 (!!!) resist modifier to MR, I hope you can reach 350-400 in MR to resist them.<br>
3) Necro are bad boys to play with. Remember that the shaman potions just remove 8 counters of disease or poison (if I recall correctly) so removings DoTs will take soime cast of them. Pure Blood is your friend here.<br>
4) Debuffing the necro will : lower his MR, lower is AC (lol) and lower his HP.<br>
5) Try to get a see invis buff/potion with you. If he decide to go invis you will lose him as a target. This would be stupid against a cleric as it would kill his pet, but on PvP server, some necro uses this tactic : DoT you to death then go invis and look you die slowly. As clerics are the best guys around to clear DoTs, this would be stupid, but who knows.<br>
<br>
These are the words of the wise.<br>
Regards,<br>
<br>
Klatcrane,<br>
